---
layout: base.njk
title: Blog
seoTitle: B2B GTM, SEO and Growth Marketing Blog
description: Practical guides on B2B GTM, SEO, demand generation, cold email, and growth marketing.
permalink: /blog/
---

<section>
  <h1>Blog</h1>
  <p>Practical guides on B2B GTM, SEO, demand generation, cold email, and growth marketing.</p>

  <div class="post-list">
    {% for post in collections.blog | reverse %}
      <article class="post-card">
        <h2><a href="{{ post.url }}">{{ post.data.title }}</a></h2>
        {% if post.data.description %}
          <p>{{ post.data.description }}</p>
        {% endif %}
        {% if post.data.category %}
          <small>{{ post.data.category }}</small>
        {% endif %}
      </article>
    {% endfor %}
  </div>
</section>
